{"tid":469642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果家燕姐無左粒墨，佢會唔會有今時今日既成就？","createTime":"2017-11-15T13:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T13:48:26.000Z","uid":85743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5f8df41cdb9dde0f523a26f8f6510a3fe244a7","tid":469642,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"墨痣面相：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/214300_78c477de5aac0ca049dc3accee8ee718.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F214300_78c477de5aac0ca049dc3accee8ee718.gif&h=fea02383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眉心對上：常常聽到有人說「面上無好墨」，其實面上有兩粒墨是吉的，一粒是「食墨」，另一粒就是位於眉心對上的「觀音墨」。凡有此墨的人必定菩薩心腸，不計較得失，為群眾服務，一生很多事情也能逢凶化吉，有驚無險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成就1：<br />\n長女：石祐珊（32&ndash;33歲）、二子：石耀庭（30&ndash;31歲）、三女：石耀珠（28&ndash;29歲）<br />\n<br />\n成就2：<br />\n「名古屋呀~燕窩~月餅~低卡~好食~健康~又fit D!」<br />\n<br />\n成就3：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/213813_2587809036df569f7ce0f099699d3c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F213813_2587809036df569f7ce0f099699d3c51.jpg&h=19f9928a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成就4：<br />\n《真情》「好姨」角色深入民心<br />\n<br />\n成就5：<br />\n榮獲香港特區政府頒授榮譽勳章，成為首位獲得此榮譽的女藝人<br />\n<br />\n成就6：皆大歡喜十字步<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/214050_27c88b87449694c5358eeb7c3b64df81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F214050_27c88b87449694c5358eeb7c3b64df81.jpg&h=aab080d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成就7：家燕媽媽<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/214417_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F214417_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif&h=8c6977f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/214450_754dd272c2b54d70e975d760314f1518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F214450_754dd272c2b54d70e975d760314f1518.jpg&h=16384eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f097372c21e89678c359d7f7a54fc01f64a5fe89","tid":469642,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"粒墨先係佢本體"}]}